@node konk "  VoteX v1.52 -- Conclusion -- "

  Finally, I would like to conclude the following,

 The Amiga, -unlike PCs- is a computer that can stand the test of time, a
computer that no matter how aged or old, or rusty, can out run ANY PC, ANY
day ! Evidence to that, the Amiga games that were released for classic A1200
did outrun a lot of PC games . Just sowing off with StrangersAGA to my PC
owning friends, now they are ALWAYS over at my place ... ( Wonder why ? )

 As for Daydream, it shall remain to be one of the best BBS programs
available for the Amiga, opinions might deffer, but I give NO damn !

 I will continue to create doors for Daydream, Arexx or C, and will continue
to try and stretch Daydream's already available doors, and will consider
myself the No.1 doors creator for this BBS program, providing tons of doors
for free, without any hassle . Just pure doors, for a pure program .



 I hope I made someone's day out there .. 




 --------- This door has been released on the 20th of February `98 ---------




@endnode

